2000-04-08  mkochano  <mkochano@pld-linux.org>

	* rc.d/rc.sysinit:
	- Changed 'modprobe -s midi' to 'modprobe -s synth0'. There is no module
	  'midi'.
	- Changed 'modprobe -s sound' to 'modprobe -s sound-slot-0'. This causes sound
	  card driver to be loaded.

